Package: croma
Architecture: any
Depends: libcroma-private2 (= ${binary:Version}),
         croma-common (= ${source:Version}),
         mate-desktop-common (>= 1.24),
         zenity,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
Breaks: mate-window-manager (<= 1.0.0-2),
Provides: x-window-manager,
Description: lightweight CTK+ window manager for MATE
 Croma is a small window manager, using CTK+ to do everything. It is
 developed mainly for the MATE Desktop.
 .
 This package contains the croma window manager itself.

Package: croma-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
Breaks: mate-window-manager (<= 1.0.0-2),
Description: lightweight CTK+ window manager for MATE (common files)
 Croma is a small window manager, using CTK+ to do everything. It is
 developed mainly for the MATE Desktop.
 .
 This package contains the architecture independent files.

